@startuml
title Système — Expiration des projets ACTIVE après deadline

' ------------------------------------------------------------------
' Style impression A4 (PFE FSEG) — lisibilité : polices ~11–12 pt visibles,
' DPI 240, retour à la ligne des messages. Inclure juste après la ligne title.
' Export PNG pour Word/LaTeX : viser largeur <= zone utile A4 (~17 cm).
' ------------------------------------------------------------------
scale max 1550 width
skinparam dpi 240
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam handwritten false
skinparam HyperlinkUnderline false

skinparam defaultFontSize 12
skinparam titleFontSize 16
skinparam ArrowFontSize 11
skinparam arrowThickness 1.25
skinparam wrapWidth 220
skinparam NoteFontSize 10
skinparam LegendFontSize 10
skinparam footerFontSize 10
skinparam headerFontSize 10

skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam ParticipantPadding 14
skinparam BoxPadding 8
skinparam LifeLineBorderColor #444444
skinparam LifeLineBackgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam ArrowColor #222222
skinparam ActorBorderColor #222222
skinparam ActorBackgroundColor #EEF6FF
skinparam ParticipantBorderColor #333333
skinparam ParticipantBackgroundColor #FFFFFF

skinparam DatabaseBackgroundColor #F8F8F8
skinparam EntityBackgroundColor #F8FFF8
skinparam ControlBackgroundColor #FFF8F0
skinparam BoundaryBackgroundColor #F5F5FF

actor "Système" as system
control "Planificateur (cron)" as Cron
control "API interne" as Svc
entity "MongoDB" as DB

system -> Cron : Déclenchement
Cron -> Svc : GET /internal/expire-projects (Bearer)

note over Cron, Svc
  Clôture **FUNDED** (grace + payout) : **GET /internal/close-funded-projects** (même Bearer).
end note

Svc -> DB : Projets ACTIVE non archivés, deadline < now\n(limite paginée)
DB --> Svc : projets expirés

loop chaque projet
  Svc -> DB : FailedRefundEvent OVERFUNDING non résolu ?
  DB --> Svc : blocking
  alt blocking
    Svc -> Svc : skip (compteur skippedOverfunding)
  else
    Svc -> DB : Project → CLOSED (update idempotent)
    Svc -> DB : AuditLog EXPIRE_PROJECT
    Svc -> DB : Notification créateur PROJECT_EXPIRED

    Svc -> DB : Investissements INITIATED → FAILED\n+ Transactions PENDING → FAILED\n+ notif investisseur PAYMENT_FAILED

    Svc -> DB : Investissements SUCCESS + tx SUCCEEDED\n→ tentative remboursement EXPIRY (mock provider)\n→ REFUNDED ou FailedRefundEvent

    Svc -> DB : FailedRefundEvent non résolu sur ce projet ?
    alt oui et admins connus
      Svc -> DB : Notifications admin REFUND_FAILED
    end
  end
end

Svc --> Cron : 200 { ok, summary }

legend bottom
  Implémentation : **cronService.expireProjects**. Remboursements : appel provider **inline** (pas de file BullMQ dans ce service).
end legend

@enduml
